data.description: STUNNING FORMER MODEL!! Tons of upgrades that you won't find anywhere else! Challenger Model Home in Forest Meadows is finally available again. Upgraded from Top to Bottom. Starting with the Office to your left as you walk in the front door, which includes Bead Board surround. Then additional hardwood on the entire main level. Gorgeous Living room with Fireplace and Beamed Ceilings across the Great Room, Dining Room and into the Kitchen. Top of the line new appliances in the Kitchen! Upgraded cabinets and Granite. Large walk-in pantry as well.  Upstairs has everyone's favorite Loft! Make it your Family Room, Workout Room or Kids Play Area. Double Doors into the Master Suite with lots of natural light and a 5 piece bath. Oversized Master Walk-in Closet. Fantastic Laundry Room with upgraded decor. 2 more Large bedrooms each with Walk-in Closets. 2 blocks away from an Amazing Park! Kids Jungle Gym. Picnic Pavilion. Soccer Field. Basketball Court. And a Huge Dog Park! This home has it all and is in Move-in Ready Condition!
